<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>61</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 nǐ shì wǒ jiǎo qián de dēng, nǐ shì wǒ lù shàng de guāng, zài hēi àn lǐ méi yǒu mí shī fāng xiàng;
 suī shì yōu gǔ shēn shēn, dàn wǒ bì bù zāo hài, yīn wèi shén cháng yǔ wǒ tóng zài.
 xíng zǒu yě bù pí fá, bēn pǎo yě bù kùn juàn, yé hé huá shì wǒ de lì liàng;
 wú lùn zài nǎ lǐ, wú lùn zài hé fāng, zhǔ shì wǒ dào lù shàng de guāng.</lyrics>
<title>nǐ shì wǒ jiǎo qián de dēng 迦南61</title>
</song>